headline: Jack Henry Awarded on TIME's America's Best Mid-Size Companies 2025 List
summary: Jack Henry™ (Nasdaq: JKHY) was named one of America's best mid-size companies by TIME and Statista for the second consecutive year. This list recognizes U.S. companies with revenues between $100 million and $10 billion that have shown strong revenue growth, received positive feedback from employees, and demonstrated dedication to corporate responsibility.
